title: NFL ATL: Projected starters, Bucky Brooks live!
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Projected starters, Bucky Brooks live!
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- continues its team-by-team breakdown of starting lineups across the NFL.  Elsewhere, the gang welcomes Bucky Brooks into Studio 66 to make sense of the league's post-draft landscape.
